                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8277" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0550</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1828 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">为有源头活水来：广达电子一线工人流失管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">For a Running Water: Front-line Worker Turnover Management of Guangda Electronics </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陈万思，王涛，邹怡</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华东理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江苏广达电子有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">制造业 一线员工流失 ；流失对策</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> manufacturing industry,  front-line employee turnover,  loss countermeasures</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着《中国制造2025》的正式发布，我国制造业的发展迈入了新的历史阶段。作为我国第一个十年制造强国战略行动纲领，它标志着我国制造业从高速度向高质量的重大转变。在这个关键的转型期，制造业企业面临着前所未有的挑战与机遇，而提高发展质量、实现从粗放式到精细化的转型已成为行业发展的必然要求。制造业企业的成功与市场竞争优势，离不开基层员工的辛勤付出与坚定支持。然而令人担忧的是，一线员工的离职率居高不下，已经成为国内制造型企业亟待解决的重要问题。本案例通过描述江苏广达电子有限公司基层员工的流失状况、高流失率带来的影响以及一线基层员工高流失率背后的原因，引导学生在理解员工流失模型、激励理论等相关内容的基础上，帮助学生掌握理论提炼与实践决策的能力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the announcement of &quot;Made in China 2025&quot;, our country&#39;s manufacturing industry has entered a new historical stage. As China&#39;s first 10-year strategic action program for manufacturing power, it marks a major transformation of China&#39;s manufacturing industry from high speed to high quality. In this critical transition period, manufacturing enterprises are facing unprecedented challenges and opportunities, and improving the quality of development and realizing the transformation from extensive to refined has become an inevitable requirement for the development of the industry. The success and market competitive advantage of manufacturing enterprises cannot be separated from the hard work and firm support of grassroots employees. However, it is worrying that the high turnover rate of front-line employees has become an important issue to be solved by domestic manufacturing enterprises. This case describes the loss of grass-roots employees in Jiangsu Quanta Electronics Co., LTD., the impact of the high turnover rate and the reasons behind the high turnover rate of front-line grass-roots employees, guides students to understand the employee turnover model, incentive theory and other relevant content, and helps students master the ability of theory refining and practical decision-making</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">员工离职；激励理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-04</td>
                            </tr>
